{"tid":1998513,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Kickstarter有筍耳筒project","createTime":"2020-05-02T12:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T00:09:07.000Z","uid":355301,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"960f71d8a861322f7193ade77621a49e1312be7a","tid":1998513,"uid":355301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"得閒去Kickstarter睇下，<br />\n見到呢個大和民族製嘅耳筒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kumanoisao/phonon-smb-01l-professional-monitoring-headphones\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fkumanoisao%2Fphonon-smb-01l-professional-monitoring-headphones&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3766c17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kumanoisao/phonon-smb-01l-professional-monitoring-headphones</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住上網摷吓呢個牌子嘅評價，<br />\n有人咁評價佢上一代<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.head-fi.org/threads/phonon-smb-02-holy-grail.627930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.head-fi.org%2Fthreads%2Fphonon-smb-02-holy-grail.627930%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=4225bf66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.head-fi.org/threads/phonon-smb-02-holy-grail.627930/</a><br />\n//...Cymbals decay with such a natural and seductive trail that makes you wonder why are these phones only 350.00.  Overall, the sound is balanced, FULL, WARM, and full of details and very refined. It is a closed headphone so, soundstage is quite limited but nevertheless it does an amazing job at recreating spatial dimension around instruments. I had my AKG K550's with me  to audition and i immediately put them away in embarassment because the sound from those were so thin and frail and shrill to listen - that's AKG sound for everyone. not enjoyable. so, I was sold,  i picked up the PHONON SMB-02 and have not regretted ever since. I prefer these to the HD650's because of the neutrality of the sound. So, clear. these are TRUE STUDIO HEADPHONES. ....<br />\n...<br />\nIt is 350.00 but it absolutely without question performs like a 1000.00 pair of headphones at least, hint hint.. hd800.. don't own but brother does and I got to A/B them. while the hd800 is an open air design it sounds more spacious but musicality is on par with the PHONONS are far as pacing, details, warmth, texture. how do I end this, ok.. here it does.. it's one of those phones where you put it on and listen to your most familiar and most favorite recordings and find yourself hearing new things and tapping your feet and SMILING!!!...//<br />\n<br />\n而家佢新一代眾籌緊，好似好抵屌，有興趣嘅巴打可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcb2e54ad389590b4f17e9a84359d2dd75eb33e","tid":1998513,"uid":123848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"槍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324d3856cf4080a8f6468de53298b8e467febeec","tid":1998513,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8bcb2e54ad389590b4f17e9a84359d2dd75eb33e","tid":1998513,"uid":123848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"槍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"100%"},{"pid":"e06c4da4ce96df1a1563e72cdeaf0b642c78f51a","tid":1998513,"uid":355301,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"324d3856cf4080a8f6468de53298b8e467febeec","tid":1998513,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8bcb2e54ad389590b4f17e9a84359d2dd75eb33e","tid":1998513,"uid":123848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"槍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"100%"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"你信一間細到豆膶嘅日本公司 連